data.description:
Step inside this trendy and beautifully appointed 4 bedroom home! As you enter, the open concept floor plan is a dream, with wood laminate flooring throughout, recessed lighting, ceiling fan, open kitchen, stainless steel appliances, and more! The primary bedroom boasts a trey ceiling, ceiling fan, plush carpet, huge walk in closet and private bath. Three additional bedrooms with ceiling fans for space to unwind. Need plenty of storage? Bedrooms all feature large closets, there is an additional bonus space and a 2 car garage! Fenced in backyard with a refreshing above ground pool for your enjoyment! Pets allowed with owner approval. Applications are located on the Spence Properties website.MySpenceProperties.com for more information.
